Most importantly, the first amputees to use this biomechanically designed walking foot have loved it from the first steps.

We believe that the key to a long term happy and healthy patient is quality healthcare that makes both you and your child feel at ease. It is our goal to promote your child’s happiness and reduce tears, even when they have to come in for a doctor’s visit!
